SELECT
   LOWER(CONCAT (
			SUBSTR(HEX(loc_id), 1, 8)
			,'-'
			,SUBSTR(HEX(loc_id), 9, 4)
			,'-'
			,SUBSTR(HEX(loc_id), 13, 4)
			,'-'
			,SUBSTR(HEX(loc_id), 17, 4)
			,'-'
			,SUBSTR(HEX(loc_id), 21)
			)) AS loc_id,	
    LOWER(CONCAT (
			SUBSTR(HEX(org_id), 1, 8)
			,'-'
			,SUBSTR(HEX(org_id), 9, 4)
			,'-'
			,SUBSTR(HEX(org_id), 13, 4)
			,'-'
			,SUBSTR(HEX(org_id), 17, 4)
			,'-'
			,SUBSTR(HEX(org_id), 21)
			)) AS org_id,
			
loc_contact_name,
loc_created,
loc_email,
loc_email_2,
loc_modified,
loc_phone,
loc_send_to_collections,
loc_delay_days,
loc_phone_extension,
loc_phone_country_code,
tzl_id
FROM hard_collection.location
WHERE loc_modified >= STR_TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i ')
AND loc_modified < STR_TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i ')

SELECT

	,LOWER(CONCAT (SUBSTR(HEX(mtre_from_loc_id), 1, 8),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(mtre_from_loc_id), 9, 4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(mtre_from_loc_id), 13, 4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(mtre_from_loc_id), 17, 4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(mtre_from_loc_id), 21))) AS mtre_from_loc_id

	,mtre_from_client_number
	,mtre_to_client_number
	,LOWER(CONCAT (SUBSTR(HEX(mtre_from_agrm_id), 1, 8),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(mtre_from_agrm_id), 9, 4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(mtre_from_agrm_id), 13, 4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(mtre_from_agrm_id), 17, 4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(mtre_from_agrm_id), 21))) AS mtre_from_agrm_id
	,LOWER(CONCAT (SUBSTR(HEX(mtre_to_agrm_id), 1, 8),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(mtre_to_agrm_id), 9, 4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(mtre_to_agrm_id), 13, 4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(mtre_to_agrm_id), 17, 4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(mtre_to_agrm_id), 21))) AS mtre_to_agrm_id
	,mtre_from_agrm_number
	,mtre_to_agrm_number
	,mtre_from_transfer_location_type
	,mtre_to_transfer_location_type
	,mtre_transfer_status
	,mtre_transfer_type
	,mtre_request_source
	,mtre_created
	,mtre_modified
	,mtre_modified
FROM member_transfer.member_transfer_record
WHERE  mtre_modified >= STR_TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i')
AND    mtre_modified < STR_TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i')

FROM organization.note_reference
WHERE nr_modified >= STR_TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i')
AND nr_modified < STR_TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i')

SELECT LOWER(CONCAT(SUBSTR(HEX(org_id),1,8),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(org_id),9,4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(org_id),13,4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(org_id),17,4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(org_id),21))) AS org_id,
       LOWER(CONCAT(SUBSTR(HEX(nt_id),1,8),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nt_id),9,4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nt_id),13,4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nt_id),17,4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nt_id),21))) AS nt_id,
       nt_created,
       nt_modified,
       LOWER(CONCAT(SUBSTR(HEX(nac_id),1,8),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nac_id),9,4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nac_id),13,4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nac_id),17,4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nac_id),21))) AS nac_id,
       nt_text,
	   nt_author_first_name,
       nt_author_last_name,
       nt_author_user_name,
       nt_author_alias,
	   nt_date,
       LOWER(CONCAT(SUBSTR(HEX(loc_id),1,8),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(loc_id),9,4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(loc_id),13,4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(loc_id),17,4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(loc_id),21))) AS loc_id,
       nt_message
	   FROM organization.note 
WHERE nt_modified >= STR_TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i')
AND nt_modified < STR_TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i')

SELECT 
LOWER(CONCAT (SUBSTR(HEX(nt_id), 1, 8),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nt_id), 9, 4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nt_id), 13, 4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nt_id), 17, 4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nt_id), 21))) AS nt_id 
,LOWER(CONCAT (SUBSTR(HEX(nac_id), 1, 8),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nac_id), 9, 4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nac_id), 13, 4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nac_id), 17, 4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(nac_id), 21))) AS nac_id 
,nnac_created
,nnac_modified
FROM  organization.note_note_action_code
WHERE nnac_modified >= STR_TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i')
AND nnac_modified < STR_TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i')

SELECT 
LOWER(CONCAT(SUBSTR(HEX(org_id),1,8),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(org_id),9,4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(org_id),13,4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(org_id),17,4),'-',SUBSTR(HEX(org_id),21))) AS org_id,
ob_color_scheme,
ob_created,
ob_modified,
ob_logo_path,
ob_primary_message,
ob_secondary_message
FROM organization.organization_branding
WHERE ob_modified >= STR_TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowStart, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i')
AND ob_modified < STR_TO_DATE('@{formatDateTime(pipeline().parameters.windowEnd, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm' )}', '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i')
